title: MWDB
description:
MWDB is an opensource malware collector and databases. https://mwdb.readthedocs.io/en/latest/user-guide/1-Introduction-to-MWDB.html.
This connector ingests malware feeds in order to import Observables and Indicator related to malware and their configurations.
This connector was built using the TAXII2 connector for OpenCTI as a base.
